pricing_plans.plan_description:
Unlimited messages and web push notifications. Optimal Package is valid for 30 consecutive days from the date of activation.

$35/month - up to 10,000 contacts;
$78/month - up to 25,000 contacts;
$135/month - up to 50,000 contacts;
$450/month - up to 250,000 contacts;

initial_reviews.review_content:
What do you like best about eSputnik?
Various communication channels, including mobile, web push, emails, and messengers, have significantly contributed to increased customer engagement. Using omnichannel has allowed us to strengthen customer relationships and increase loyalty and trust. As a result, we receive a higher number of repeat orders from satisfied and loyal customers, confirming our strategy's effectiveness.

What do you dislike about eSputnik?
No shortcomings were found, eSputnik CDP is the best solution for omnichannel interaction with each customer.

What problems is eSputnik solving and how is that benefiting you?
eSputnik Omnichannel CDP solves goals:
- understanding customers and their needs;
- data collection;
- personalization;
- seamless customer communication across all channels.

review_question_answers.answer:
eSputnik Omnichannel CDP solves goals:
- understanding customers and their needs;
- data collection;
- personalization;
- seamless customer communication across all channels.

With eSputnik we managed to:

- set up personalized omnichannel marketing campaigns;
- unify all customer's data in one place;
- save a lot of time thanks to automated workflows and machine learning.

"The functionality of this omnichannel system goes beyond a regular ESP or standard email marketing tool. eSputnik is a veritable CDP platform which provides a lot of unique features for Ecommerce:

- Advanced data collection and deep contact list segmentation;
- Profile unification features: personalizaed product recommendations, triggered messages etc;
- AI-based algorithms for launching automated campaigns;
- Multilingual transactional messages etc.

In addition, eSputnik can be easily integrated with almost any CRM system via API, ApiX-Drive or Zapier. A really good tool from ukrainian developpers!"

- can be integrated with Zapier, Google Sheets and Facebook Ads Manager;
- contains plenty of interesting features like multilingual campaigns, mobile pushes, Viber messages, etc.;
- great support services;
- simple and convenient drag and drop editor.

I like how easy it is to create email templates and translate them into other languages. This tool is an ideal solution for email campaigns and web push notifications.

